1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,025
Have you ever been looking for a hat,

2
00:00:02,025 --> 00:00:03,990
and find out that you're already wearing it.

3
00:00:03,990 --> 00:00:05,565
Or looking for your keys,

4
00:00:05,565 --> 00:00:07,470
and find out there in your back pocket.

5
00:00:07,470 --> 00:00:09,165
Or looking for your backpack,

6
00:00:09,165 --> 00:00:11,295
and you find out that it's on your back.

7
00:00:11,295 --> 00:00:14,850
Turns out losing your remote is the same problem.

8
00:00:14,850 --> 00:00:19,050
This chart highlights the seven places your remote is likely to be.

9
00:00:19,050 --> 00:00:21,825
The top place is in your hand.

10
00:00:21,825 --> 00:00:25,575
The least likely place that it is, is lost forever.

11
00:00:25,575 --> 00:00:28,290
But before you think you are one of those two people,

12
00:00:28,290 --> 00:00:30,390
make sure you check under the couch,

13
00:00:30,390 --> 00:00:32,865
next to the TV, in the fridge,

14
00:00:32,865 --> 00:00:34,170
in your shirt pocket,

15
00:00:34,170 --> 00:00:35,445
and under the rug.

16
00:00:35,445 --> 00:00:38,655
Before you blame the dog for eating your remote or thinking

17
00:00:38,655 --> 00:00:42,255
alien came from space and stole your remote, check your hand.

18
00:00:42,255 --> 00:00:45,630
It's unlikely your remote is gone forever.

